    "(AWS_SECRET|AWS_ACCESS|GCP_SERVICE|AZURE_CLIENT)",
    "(STRIPE|PAYPAL|SENDGRID|TWILIO|SLACK)_?(API|SECRET|KEY|TOKEN)"
